      <category domain="https://adilhyz.github.io/categories/os/">OS</category>
      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;heading-element&#34; id=&#34;android&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Android&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#android&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ya, Android memanglah populer dikalangan pengguna smartphone, &lt;a href=&#34;https://gs.statcounter.com/os-market-share/mobile/worldwide&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;external nofollow noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;data&lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; menunjukan bahwa Android menduduki peringkat pertama pengguna smartphone terbanyak di Dunia. Android merupakan sistem operasi sumber terbuka yang dikembangkan oleh &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.android.com/&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;external nofollow noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;Google&lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; dan &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.openhandsetalliance.com/android_overview.html&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;external nofollow noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;Open Handset Alliance&lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  Android dirancang untuk perangkat ponsel pintar dan tablet.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
